<b>

Win a visit from Fred Langa and&nbsp;his&nbsp;hog

</b><br></font><font color="black" face="Arial,Sans-serif" size="2">

Windows Secrets editor Fred Langa (at left in helmet) is taking 
the summer off to cruise around North America on his beloved 
motorcycle. He's going to select at least four subscribers in the 
contiguous United States and southern Canadian provinces to win one 
of his renowned Housecalls, as determined by our
<a href="http://WindowsSecrets.com/links/p3472n61w1axd/d3e6f3h/?url=WindowsSecrets.com%2Fhousecall-rules"><u>contest rules</u></a>. 
If you're selected, Fred will roar 
up on his bike and spend the day optimizing your PC, testing for 
viruses, and more. Use the links below for more information or 
to enter the contest. (You must enter by Apr. 25, 2007.) 
&#8212;<i>Brian Livingston, Editorial Director</i><br><small><br></small>

